**Object components:**

```ts
{
  id: 'object-floating-sphere',
  name: 'Floating Sphere',
  description: 'Sphere with gentle float animation. Good as a central focus object.',
  buildFn: `
    function build(scene, palette, seed) {
      const group = new THREE.Group();
      const geo = new THREE.SphereGeometry(1.5, 32, 32);
      const mat = new THREE.MeshStandardMaterial({
        color: palette[0],
        roughness: 0.3,
