  This produces better quality than generating Three.js from scratch.
  Choose lighting, camera, objects, and environment from the available
  components. Add custom code only for unique requirements.
  
  Available lighting: ${COMPONENT_IDS.lighting.join(', ')}
  Available cameras: ${COMPONENT_IDS.cameras.join(', ')}
