  input_schema: {
    sceneId: 'string',
    lighting: 'string — component id',
    camera: 'string — component id',
    objects: 'string[] — 1-3 object component ids',
    environment: 'string | null — environment component id',
    customCode: 'string | null — additional Three.js code to run after setup',
    data: 'object | null — data for data-viz components'
  }
}
```

Still keep `generate_three_layer` for cases where no component fits,
but instruct the agent to prefer `assemble_three_scene`.

